				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-5-T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-gi%C3%A1m-Giang-H%E1%BA%A1-L%C3%BD-c%C3%B4ng-Ung/poem-Qu1ia6IYu7v8HffB5dNOyA">Bát ai thi kỳ 5 - Tặng bí thư giám Giang Hạ Lý công Ung - 八哀詩其五－贈秘書監江夏李公邕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/B%E1%BB%95-x%C3%A0-gi%E1%BA%A3-thuy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-6rOlVuds9Kh1YCFFEgqOPQ">Bổ xà giả thuyết - 捕蛇者說</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%93i-tr%E1%BA%A1o/poem-qeP_kb_yUSYlzh8F95bgrQ">Hồi trạo - 回棹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-tam-lang-trung-C%E1%BB%A9/poem-lATfZIOTSPPfR_TtCqM3nA">Ký Tiết tam lang trung Cứ - 寄薛三郎中據</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1n-s%C6%A1n-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ti%C3%AAu/poem-lZEK-WJ5cMRpUVbXMXSc_g">Lôi (Đại hạn sơn nhạc tiêu) - 雷（大旱山嶽燋）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99ng-L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-t3J6Fcmdaf3mpdvJwS2fsg">Mộng Lý Bạch kỳ 1 - 夢李白其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-JuEDCLEaOpQ7FrCxZOZzwA">Ngoạ bệnh kỳ 1 - 臥病其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tu%C3%BD-Quang/T%E1%BA%B7ng-An-Nam-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%A7n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Q1U4A_BvJac71-a5ZAFYfw">Tặng An Nam quốc sứ thần kỳ 1 - 贈安南國使臣其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tu%C3%BD-Quang/author-b_59yjbwra73kXanqja7Ow">Lý Tuý Quang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-tr%C3%ADch-M%C3%A2n-trung/poem-zGhyYAaXIoikgkNKc5W2CQ">Tống Trịnh thị ngự trích Mân trung - 送鄭侍禦謫閩中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/author-daTT9TQ-QJ39piO86WPo5Q">Cao Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-quan-ki%E1%BA%BFn-mai-l%E1%BB%A5c-ng%C3%B4n/poem-FkgysmW84eBOzPuhWZZ3TA">Tuyết quan kiến mai lục ngôn - 雪關見梅六言</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-eBGdtm3O4c2NQ7sIhikeXg">Dương Thận</a>)<br></div>	</div>
